---
// Diagram 6 — MCP Blindness: Three States
---

<figure class="my-10">
  <svg
    role="img"
    aria-labelledby="mcpTitle mcpDesc"
    viewBox="0 0 680 340"
    class="w-full h-auto max-w-3xl mx-auto"
  >
    <title id="mcpTitle">Three Tiers of Agent Accessibility</title>
    <desc id="mcpDesc">
      Three progression cards — Not Accessible, Agent-Accessible (MCP wrapper),
      and Agent-Native — showing the increase in ceiling and decrease in overhead
      as platforms invest in agent-native primitives.
    </desc>

    <defs>
      <marker id="mcp-arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="9" refY="5" markerWidth="9" markerHeight="9" orient="auto">
        <path d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 Z" fill="#1A1A18" />
      </marker>
    </defs>

    <!-- State 1: Not Accessible (gray / muted) -->
    <g>
      <rect x="20" y="40" width="200" height="220" rx="12" fill="#FAFAF8" stroke="#D3D1C7" stroke-width="2" />
      <text x="120" y="72" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-weight="700" font-size="14" fill="#5F5E5A">
        Not accessible
      </text>
      <text x="120" y="94" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#5F5E5A">
        no MCP · silent failures
      </text>
      <line x1="40" y1="110" x2="200" y2="110" stroke="#D3D1C7" />
      <g font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#1A1A18">
        <text x="40" y="140">Overhead: ~100%</text>
        <text x="40" y="164">Ceiling: none</text>
        <text x="40" y="188">Auth: human-only</text>
      </g>
      <text x="120" y="234" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#5F5E5A" font-style="italic">
        Agents fabricate.
      </text>
    </g>

    <!-- State 2: Agent-Accessible (amber) -->
    <g>
      <rect x="240" y="40" width="200" height="220" rx="12" fill="#FAEEDA" stroke="#854F0B" stroke-width="2" />
      <text x="340" y="72" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-weight="700" font-size="14" fill="#854F0B">
        Agent-accessible
      </text>
      <text x="340" y="94" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#854F0B">
        MCP wrapper · human-speed API
      </text>
      <line x1="260" y1="110" x2="420" y2="110" stroke="#854F0B" />
      <g font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#1A1A18">
        <text x="260" y="140">Overhead: ~70–80%</text>
        <text x="260" y="164">Ceiling: ~5×</text>
        <text x="260" y="188">Auth: session-based</text>
      </g>
      <text x="340" y="234" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#854F0B" font-style="italic">
        Starting point, not finish line.
      </text>
    </g>

    <!-- State 3: Agent-Native (teal) -->
    <g>
      <rect x="460" y="40" width="200" height="220" rx="12" fill="#E1F5EE" stroke="#0F6E56" stroke-width="2" />
      <text x="560" y="72" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-weight="700" font-size="14" fill="#0F6E56">
        Agent-native
      </text>
      <text x="560" y="94" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#0F6E56">
        purpose-built primitives
      </text>
      <line x1="480" y1="110" x2="640" y2="110" stroke="#0F6E56" />
      <g font-family="JetBrains Mono, monospace" font-size="11" fill="#1A1A18">
        <text x="480" y="140">Overhead: ~30%</text>
        <text x="480" y="164">Ceiling: structurally higher</text>
        <text x="480" y="188">Auth: programmatic token</text>
      </g>
      <text x="560" y="234" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="11" fill="#0F6E56" font-style="italic">
        Compounding advantage.
      </text>
    </g>

    <!-- Progress arrow across bottom -->
    <g stroke="#1A1A18" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none" marker-end="url(#mcp-arrow)">
      <line x1="40" y1="300" x2="640" y2="300" />
    </g>
    <text x="340" y="324" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Inter, sans-serif" font-size="12" fill="#1A1A18" font-weight="600">
      Investment required →
    </text>
  </svg>
  <figcaption class="text-sm text-muted text-center mt-3 italic">
    MCP makes a platform agent-accessible. Agent-native makes it fast enough to compete.
  </figcaption>
</figure>
